{
  "spec": {
    "title": "CSS Route Matching",
    "url": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "route-location/match",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#route-location-match",
      "html": "A <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-route-location\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-route-location②\">&lt;route-location&gt;</a> is defined to\n<dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"route-location\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"route-location-match\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">match</dfn> a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url\">URL</a>-or-null <var>input</var> if <var>input</var> is non-null,\nand the corresponding statement:",
      "rationale": ".switch",
      "steps": [
        {
          "operation": "switch",
          "steps": [
            {
              "case": "the <route-location> is a <route-name>",
              "html": "<p>The <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern\">URL pattern</a> represented by the <a class=\"css\" data-link-type=\"maybe\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#at-ruledef-route\" id=\"ref-for-at-ruledef-route\">@route</a> rule referenced by the name <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#match-url-pattern-with-params\" id=\"ref-for-match-url-pattern-with-params\">matches</a> <var>input</var> given the provided <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-url-pattern-param-matcher\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-url-pattern-param-matcher②\">&lt;url-pattern-param-matcher&gt;</a> (if exists).</p>"
            },
            {
              "case": "the <route-location> is a <url-pattern()>",
              "html": "<p>The provided <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern①\">URL pattern</a> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#match-url-pattern-with-params\" id=\"ref-for-match-url-pattern-with-params①\">matches</a> <var>input</var> given the provided <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-url-pattern-param-matcher\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-url-pattern-param-matcher③\">&lt;url-pattern-param-matcher&gt;</a> (if exists).</p>"
            },
            {
              "case": "the <route-location> is a <url>",
              "html": "<p>The provided <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url①\">URL</a> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url-equals\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url-equals\">equals</a> <var>input</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "match URL pattern with params",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#match-url-pattern-with-params",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"match-url-pattern-with-params\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">match URL pattern with params</dfn>\n  given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern②\">URL pattern</a> <var>urlPattern</var>,\n  a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url②\">URL</a> <var>input</var>,\n  and an optional <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-url-pattern-param-matcher\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-url-pattern-param-matcher④\">&lt;url-pattern-param-matcher&gt;</a> <var>paramMatcher</var> (default null):",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>result</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern-match\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern-match\">matching</a> <var>urlPattern</var> against <var>input</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>result</var> is null, return false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>paramMatcher</var> is null, return true.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>paramMap</var> be null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>paramMatcher</var> is `all from ` <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values-4/#url-value\" id=\"ref-for-url-value③\" title=\"Expands to: local url flag\">&lt;url&gt;</a>, then:</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>urlMatchResult</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern-match\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern-match①\">matching</a> <var>urlPattern</var> against the URL represented by the <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values-4/#url-value\" id=\"ref-for-url-value④\" title=\"Expands to: local url flag\">&lt;url&gt;</a> in <var>paramMatcher</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>urlMatchResult</var> is null, return false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>paramMap</var> to <var>urlMatchResult</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#combined-url-pattern-result-groups\" id=\"ref-for-combined-url-pattern-result-groups\">combined URL pattern result groups</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Otherwise, set <var>paramMap</var> to an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-map\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-map\">ordered map</a> that reflects the <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-url-pattern-param\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-url-pattern-param②\">&lt;url-pattern-param&gt;</a> entries in <var>paramMatcher</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>combinedResult</var> be the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#combined-url-pattern-result-groups\" id=\"ref-for-combined-url-pattern-result-groups①\">combined URL pattern result groups</a> of <var>result</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate\">For each</a> (<var>groupName</var>, <var>groupValue</var>) in <var>paramMap</var>:</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>combinedResult</var>[<var>groupName</var>] does not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists\">exists</a> or is not <var>groupValue</var>, return false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return true.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "combined URL pattern result groups",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#combined-url-pattern-result-groups",
      "html": "To get the <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"combined-url-pattern-result-groups\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">combined URL pattern result groups</dfn> of a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dictdef-urlpatternresult\" id=\"ref-for-dictdef-urlpatternresult\">URLPatternResult</a></code> <var>result</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>combinedResult</var> be a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-map\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-map①\">ordered map</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate①\">For each</a> <var>key</var> in <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlpatternresult-protocol\" id=\"ref-for-dom-urlpatternresult-protocol\">protocol</a></code>, <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlpatternresult-hostname\" id=\"ref-for-dom-urlpatternresult-hostname\">hostname</a></code>, <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlpatternresult-port\" id=\"ref-for-dom-urlpatternresult-port\">port</a></code>, <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlpatternresult-pathname\" id=\"ref-for-dom-urlpatternresult-pathname\">pathname</a></code>, <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlpatternresult-search\" id=\"ref-for-dom-urlpatternresult-search\">search</a></code>, and <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlpatternresult-hash\" id=\"ref-for-dom-urlpatternresult-hash\">hash</a></code>:</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>component</var> be <var>result</var>[<var>key</var>].</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate②\">For each</a> (<var>name</var>, <var>value</var>) in <var>component</var>[<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlpatterncomponentresult-groups\" id=\"ref-for-dom-urlpatterncomponentresult-groups\">groups</a></code>]:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-set\" id=\"ref-for-map-set\">set</a> <var>combinedResult</var>[<var>name</var>] = <var>value</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>combinedResult</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "create a URL pattern for url-pattern()",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#create-a-url-pattern-for-url-pattern",
      "html": "The steps of the <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"create-a-url-pattern-for-url-pattern\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">create a URL pattern for url-pattern()</dfn> algorithm,\ngiven a string <var>arg</var> and\nan optional <var>baseURLSpecifier</var>\nwhich can be <span class=\"css\">document</span>, <span class=\"css\">stylesheet</span>, or a URL, are:",
      "rationale": "let",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>baseURL</var> be the result of\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#create-a-url-for-a-base-descriptor\" id=\"ref-for-create-a-url-for-a-base-descriptor①\">create a URL for a base descriptor</a> given <var>baseURLSpecifier</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern-create\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern-create①\">create a URL pattern</a> given\n<var>arg</var>, <var>baseURL</var>, and an empty <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-map\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-map②\">map</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "create a URL for a base descriptor",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#create-a-url-for-a-base-descriptor",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"create-a-url-for-a-base-descriptor\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">create a URL for a base descriptor</dfn> algorithm, given\nan optional <var>baseURLSpecifier</var>\nwhich can be <span class=\"css\">document</span>, <span class=\"css\">stylesheet</span>, or a URL, is:",
      "rationale": ".switch",
      "steps": [
        {
          "operation": "switch",
          "steps": [
            {
              "case": "if baseURLSpecifier is not present or is stylesheet",
              "html": "<p>the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values-4/#style-resource-base-url\" id=\"ref-for-style-resource-base-url\">style resource base URL</a> of\nthe rule or declaration block containing the <a class=\"css\" data-link-type=\"maybe\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#funcdef-url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-funcdef-url-pattern⑧\">url-pattern()</a> function.</p>"
            },
            {
              "case": "if baseURLSpecifier is document",
              "html": "<p>the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/urls-and-fetching.html#document-base-url\" id=\"ref-for-document-base-url\">document base URL</a> of the document</p>"
            },
            {
              "case": "if baseURLSpecifier is a URL",
              "html": "<p><var>baseURLSpecifier</var></p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "serialize a url-pattern() function",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#serialize-a-url-pattern-function",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-export=\"\" id=\"serialize-a-url-pattern-function\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">serialize a <a class=\"css\" data-link-type=\"maybe\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#funcdef-url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-funcdef-url-pattern①①\">url-pattern()</a> function</dfn> <var>f</var>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-1/#css-serialize-a-function\" id=\"ref-for-css-serialize-a-function\">serialize a function</a> <var>f</var>,\nusing <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-1/#serialize-a-string\" id=\"ref-for-serialize-a-string\">serialize a string</a> on the single argument\nto serialize <var>f</var>’s contents.",
      "rationale": "To <dfn>"
    },
    {
      "name": "current navigation state",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-navigation-state",
      "html": "To get the <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"current-navigation-state\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">current navigation state</dfn> of a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document\">Document</a></code> <var>document</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>document</var> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#fully-active\" id=\"ref-for-fully-active\">fully active</a>, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>navigation</var> be <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global\">relevant global object</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window-navigation-api\" id=\"ref-for-window-navigation-api\">navigation API</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>activation</var> be <var>navigation</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigation-activation\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigation-activation\">activation</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>document</var> has not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsing-the-web.html#has-been-revealed\" id=\"ref-for-has-been-revealed\">been revealed</a>:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>activation</var> is null, return null.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#assert\" id=\"ref-for-assert\">Assert</a>: <var>activation</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-entry\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-entry\">entry</a></code> is not null.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Return a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state\">navigation state</a> whose\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-old-url\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-old-url\">old URL</a> is <var>activation</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-from\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-from\">from</a></code>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-url\">url</a></code>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-new-url\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-new-url\">new URL</a> is <var>activation</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-entry\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-entry①\">entry</a></code>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-url①\">url</a></code>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-type\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-type\">type</a> is <var>activation</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-navigationtype\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-navigationtype\">navigationType</a></code>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-old-index\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-old-index②\">old index</a> is <var>activation</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-from\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-from①\">from</a></code>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-index\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-index\">index</a></code>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-new-index\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-new-index②\">new index</a> is <var>activation</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-entry\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-entry②\">entry</a></code>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-index\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-index①\">index</a></code>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-phase\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-phase①\">phase</a> is `committed`,\nand <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-source-element\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-source-element①\">source element</a> is null.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>navigateEvent</var> be the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#ongoing-navigate-event\" id=\"ref-for-ongoing-navigate-event\">ongoing navigate event</a> of <var>navigation</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>phase</var> be `loading`.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>navigateEvent</var> is null and <var>navigation</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#traversing-navigate-event\" id=\"ref-for-traversing-navigate-event\">traversing navigate event</a> is not null:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>navigateEvent</var> to <var>navigation</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#traversing-navigate-event\" id=\"ref-for-traversing-navigate-event①\">traversing navigate event</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>phase</var> to `ready`.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>navigateEvent</var> is null, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state①\">navigation state</a> whose\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-old-url\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-old-url①\">old URL</a> is <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document-url\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-url\">URL</a>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-new-url\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-new-url①\">new URL</a> is <var>navigateEvent</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigateevent-destination\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigateevent-destination\">destination</a></code>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationdestination-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationdestination-url\">url</a></code>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-type\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-type①\">type</a> is <var>ongoingNavigateEvent</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigateevent-navigationtype\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigateevent-navigationtype\">navigationType</a></code>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-old-index\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-old-index③\">old index</a> is <var>navigation</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#navigation-current-entry\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-current-entry\">current entry</a>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-index\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-index②\">index</a></code>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-new-index\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-new-index③\">new index</a> is <var>navigateEvent</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigateevent-destination\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigateevent-destination①\">destination</a></code>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationdestination-index\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationdestination-index\">index</a></code>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-phase\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-phase②\">phase</a> is <var>phase</var>,\nand <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-source-element\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-source-element②\">source element</a> is <var>ongoingNavigateEvent</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigateevent-sourceelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigateevent-sourceelement①\">sourceElement</a></code>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "current navigation URL",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-navigation-url",
      "html": "To get the <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"current-navigation-url\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">current navigation URL</dfn> given a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document①\">Document</a></code> <var>document</var> and a <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-navigation-relation\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-navigation-relation④\">&lt;navigation-relation&gt;</a> <var>relation</var>:",
      "rationale": "let",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>state</var> be <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-navigation-state\" id=\"ref-for-current-navigation-state⑤\">current navigation state</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>state</var> is null, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return the result of switching on <var>relation</var>:</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "current navigation URL",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-navigation-url",
      "html": "To get the <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"current-navigation-url\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">current navigation URL</dfn> given a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document①\">Document</a></code> <var>document</var> and a <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-navigation-relation\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-navigation-relation④\">&lt;navigation-relation&gt;</a> <var>relation</var>:",
      "rationale": ".switch",
      "steps": [
        {
          "operation": "switch",
          "steps": [
            {
              "case": "to",
              "html": "<p><var>state</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-new-url\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-new-url②\">new URL</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "case": "from",
              "html": "<p><var>state</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-old-url\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-old-url②\">old URL</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "case": "at",
              "html": "<p><var>state</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-new-url\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-new-url③\">new URL</a> if <var>state</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-phase\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-phase③\">phase</a> is `committed`; Otherwise <var>state</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-old-url\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-old-url③\">old URL</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "case": "with",
              "html": "<p><var>state</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-old-url\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-old-url④\">old URL</a> if <var>state</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-phase\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-phase④\">phase</a> is `committed`; Otherwise <var>state</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-new-url\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-new-url④\">new URL</a>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "current navigation type",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-navigation-type",
      "html": "To get the <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"current-navigation-type\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">current navigation type</dfn> of a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document\">document</a> <var>document</var>:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-navigation-state\" id=\"ref-for-current-navigation-state⑥\">current navigation state</a> is non-null, return its <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#navigation-state-type\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-state-type②\">type</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return null.</p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}